{"tid":2001654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(日本社會悲劇) 生活在車裡的人 在停車場的一角","createTime":"2020-05-04T16:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T16:30:21.000Z","uid":182127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"afca16371e7284f59f6eb55c741cb0bd999d51a2","tid":2001654,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/nhkworld/zt/ondemand/video/4001351/?cid=wohk-fb-na_gc_vod_Invisible_Homeless_zt_ad-202005-001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnhkworld%2Fzt%2Fondemand%2Fvideo%2F4001351%2F%3Fcid%3Dwohk-fb-na_gc_vod_Invisible_Homeless_zt_ad-202005-001&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1i%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=ed948d19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/nhkworld/zt/ondemand/video/4001351/?cid=wohk-fb-na_gc_vod_Invisible_Homeless_zt_ad-202005-001</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本全國各地有1000多處被稱作&ldquo;公路休息站&rdquo;的商業設施，開車出行的人們可以在此購物、小憩。白天，這裡人來人往，生意興隆，而到了夜間，卻面貌全非。在停車場裡，有不少長期&ldquo;生活在汽車裡的人&rdquo;，駕車輾轉於各地的&ldquo;公路休息站&rdquo;。車裡滿載著他們的所有家當，他們在狹小的車內空間和衣而睡。通過對他們進行採訪了解到，他們每個人都有自己的苦衷，有的是因為&ldquo;收入來源只有年金，支付不起房租&rdquo;；也有是的&ldquo;為了躲避家庭暴力&rdquo;，原因各不相同。&ldquo;生活在汽車裡的人&rdquo;遠離現實社会，輾轉徬徨。現實社會中到底發生了什麼呢？通過記者的隨行採訪，剖析社會的深層問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完好Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc47f1a0b3c76f15e30dd39cc0236c663e5ddad","tid":2001654,"uid":182222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"對比起香港<br />\n呢D真係濕濕碎"}]}